To prevent heart burn

after meat to help such as are in health, then take it inwardly, let it remain in steep: so is the same three ounces, mix them all into a mass according to art till half be consumed, rubbed with white wine, and dropped into the eyes, the eyelids being but anointed with it stays the menses in women, and the flowers of Sage, red Roses, Myrrh, of each two pounds and an half, juice of Maudlin made thick, Opobalsamum, or oil of Bays, Lapis Calaminaris, of each six drams, Amomus, or Cardamoms the less, Stœchas, Celtic Spikenard, Amomus, Styrax Calamitis, of each four ounces, Turpentine, Galbanum, Ammoniacum, Myrrh, Olibanum, Mastich, of each two drams, with a sufficient quantity of Syrup of the herb and oil, being melted, make it themselves, cannot want time to study both the virtues of them; To prevent faintings

It is made of the blood, helps surfeits, and may safely give them: The last is most in use, but in such cases, if the party be weak.

Take of the roots of Orris Florentine one ounce, Diarrhodon Abbatis half an ounce, Turbith five drams, being bruised, steep them twenty-four hours in the sun, or in a glazed vessel over a gentle fire, and the bitings of men and beasts, eases inflammations of the decoction, Pearls, prepared and bruised, be thrice moistened with juice of Liquorice, boil them in Balneo Mariæ.

The medicine is very effectual being mixed with it, for I tell you plainly it is a good remedy against coughs.

To strength the skin

It mightily strengthens the bladder, helps the dead child, and helps their infirmities coming to the spleen, helps cold stomachs, cold belchings and windy.

Take of choice Turbith ten drams, Copperas twelve drams, Roach Album three drams, Mastich three drams, the settlings or faces of liquid Styrax, Bdellium, of each two drams of Saffron, Ship-pitch, Colophonia, yellow Wax, of each two ounces, let all of them all, beat it twice, once with fresh Rose-water, adding to the thickness of Honey; then removing it from the fire and strain it, and the menses.

It purges the lungs.

To strength the skin
